# quickly patch alarm and sleep in a file
cat upload_center | sed 's/alarm/isinf/g' > upload_center.patched

# kill scanf
you can kill a scanf by sending NULL bytes.

# fgets
fgets reads until EOF or newline, you can exploit it to inject NULL byte in memory if you need.

# jmp esp
jmp esp is a useful gadget!

# strtol
if you give strtol a negative number it will convert it in 0xff{..}
